  "contentHtml": "<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-5e2ec0ac wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"padding-right:0;padding-left:0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-a1628350 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-ff697075 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-primary-color has-text-color has-superbfont-xxsmall-font-size\" style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:5px;text-transform:uppercase\">ABout</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-superbfont-xlarge-font-size\">Robin Berzin, MD</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-secondary-color has-text-color has-superbfont-small-font-size\">Dr. Robin Berzin is the Founder and CEO of <a href=\"https://www.parsleyhealth.com/\">Parsley Health</a>, the nation’s leading holistic medical practice designed to help people overcome chronic conditions. She founded Parsley to address the rising tide of chronic disease in America through personalized holistic medicine that puts food, lifestyle, and proactive diagnostic testing on the prescription pad next to medications. Since founding Parsley in 2016, Dr. Berzin has seen 80% of patients improve or resolve their chronic conditions within their first year of care, demonstrating the life-changing value of making modern holistic medicine accessible to everyone, anywhere. Parsley is available online nationwide.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-secondary-color has-text-color has-superbfont-small-font-size\">Dr. Berzin attended medical school at Columbia University and trained in Internal Medicine at Mount Sinai Hospital in New York City. She has been recognized by the World Economic Forum as a Tech Pioneer, named as one of the 100 most innovative women in business by <em>Inc. Magazine</em>, and praised by<em> Fast Company</em> for founding one of the World’s Most Innovative Companies. Her new book, <em><a href=\"https://robinberzinmd.com/book/\" type=\"page\" id=\"854\">State Change</a></em>, is published by Simon Element. </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-40a2a7e8 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large has-custom-border\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/CH-Fave_Robin_Portraits0424-683x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-883\" style=\"border-radius:16px\" srcset=\"https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/CH-Fave_Robin_Portraits0424-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/CH-Fave_Robin_Portraits0424-200x300.jpg 200w, https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/CH-Fave_Robin_Portraits0424-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/CH-Fave_Robin_Portraits0424-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/CH-Fave_Robin_Portraits0424-300x450.jpg 300w, https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/CH-Fave_Robin_Portraits0424-850x1274.jpg 850w, https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/CH-Fave_Robin_Portraits0424.jpg 1201w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" /></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-42a45ec0 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--superbspacing-small);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--superbspacing-small);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--superbspacing-small);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--superbspacing-small)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide press-bar-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2a77b8b3 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"border-radius:0px;padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-2715b9a4 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0px\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"175\" height=\"26\" src=\"https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/FastCompany.svg\" alt=\"FastCompany - press logo\" class=\"wp-image-322\" style=\"width:auto;height:25px\"/></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-2715b9a4 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0px\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BerzinMedia-02.svg\" alt=\"Vogue - Press logo\" class=\"wp-image-409\" style=\"width:auto;height:25px\"/></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-2715b9a4 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0px\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BerzinMedia-03.svg\" alt=\"Women's Health - Press logo\" class=\"wp-image-410\" style=\"width:auto;height:25px\"/></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-2715b9a4 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0px\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BerzinMedia-04.svg\" alt=\"New York Times - Press logo\" class=\"wp-image-411\" style=\"width:auto;height:25px\"/></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-2715b9a4 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0px\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BerzinMedia-05.svg\" alt=\"Goop - Press image\" class=\"wp-image-412\" style=\"width:auto;height:25px\"/></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-61817c03 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--superbspacing-small);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--superbspacing-small);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--superbspacing-small);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--superbspacing-small)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized has-custom-border\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"360\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/EricaChidi-edited.png\" alt=\"Erica Chidi\" class=\"wp-image-837\" style=\"border-radius:50%;width:120px;height:undefinedpx\" srcset=\"https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/EricaChidi-edited.png 360w, https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/EricaChidi-edited-300x300.png 300w, https://robinberzinmd.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/EricaChidi-edited-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-contrast-color has-text-color has-superbfont-large-font-size\">&#8220;Innovative, strategic, and wise, Dr. Berzin has created a gentle toolkit for reaching new levels of energy, clarity, and ease. Let her be your guide to a new baseline of well-being.&#8221;</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-vertical is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-4c120eef wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-contrast-color has-text-color has-superbfont-medium-font-size\">Erica Chidi</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-secondary-color has-text-color has-superbfont-medium-font-size\">co-founder &amp; CEO of LOOM</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
